Senhor Lee,

00:16:24.150 --> 00:16:25.440
Manteremos contacto.

00:16:25.440 --> 00:16:26.250
Tudo bem.

00:16:26.550 --> 00:16:26.790
Adeus.

00:16:26.790 --> 00:16:27.100
Adeus.

